# CitedBy.ai Launch Campaign Design

**Date**: 2026-02-25
**Status**: Approved
**Approach**: Product Hunt Blitz (4-week campaign)

---

## 1. Campaign Overview

**Campaign name**: "Be Cited by AI" Launch
**Goal**: Build a waitlist of 500+ email signups before opening access
**Budget**: < EUR 1,000 (mostly organic)
**Target audience**: B2B SaaS founders/marketers, digital/SEO agencies, content publishers
**Channels**: Product Hunt, Twitter/X, LinkedIn, Hacker News, Reddit, Indie Hackers, blog, email

## 2. Timeline

| Week | Phase | Focus |
|------|-------|-------|
| Week 1 | Asset Creation | Waitlist page, demo video, screenshots, PH "coming soon" page |
| Week 2 | Content & Community | Blog posts, social media content calendar, engage SEO communities |
| Week 3 | Warm-up | Daily social posts, reach out to PH supporters/hunters, early access teasers |
| Week 4 | Launch Week | PH launch (Tuesday), HN Show HN, LinkedIn viral post, Twitter thread, email blast |

**Key milestones:**
- Day -21: All assets ready (waitlist page, video, screenshots)
- Day -14: PH "Coming Soon" page live, start collecting upvote pledges
- Day -7: Pre-launch email to early supporters, final prep
- Day 0: Launch day (Tuesday, 12:01 AM PT)
- Day +7: Post-launch recap, nurture sequence begins

